title: Madonna The Hydro Glasgow UK 20thDec 2015
description:
Here is another nice bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


Madonna 
The Hydro Glasgow UK 20th Dec 2015
recorded with a Sony MZ NH1 mini disc recorder
and a ECM-719 sony mic from the second teir up to right hand side
it,s a fair recording for a big hall and Madonna fans get a bit Whhoo
Set list is incomplete as Madonna overran the curfew so Holiday is missing she performed it without the PA
so hope you enjoy it as much as my wife she loved it
